==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: ageing
<hw>ageing</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>having lived for a
relatively long (or a specified) time; not young; -- used especially of
persons. Opposite of <ant>young</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> aging, senescent, old.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

